MyDining

MyDining provides nutrition and food allergy information to help you make decisions about the foods you choose to fill your plate. Select a location below to start building your meal.

Northern Illinois University understands that students have a positive experience on campus and achieve their best academic performance when well-nourished through a community dining setting. That is why we have created the MyDining program in partnership with the School of Family, Consumer, and Nutrition Science.
